 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6125b81471d8f280eb66b75748509121cddde25c","tid":50704,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T18:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>稍為嚴重少少都破萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 係呀 想做貓奴都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚到時有咩事冇能力醫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25445d641499d9a9a676fbdcec499a47b41a954e","tid":50704,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>稍為嚴重少少都破萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 係呀 想做貓奴都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚到時有咩事冇能力醫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n領養成貓囉，慳返筆絕育費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有揀隻又肥又乖嘅唐貓，無咁多病痛，同埋可以自己沖涼剪甲慳錢。<br />\n<br />\n買隻好少少嘅糧，同溝水入啲濕糧到，飲多啲水同夠營養就無咩病痛㗎啦。<br />\n<br />\n每個月儲500，夠睇醫生㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識養記得問人，小心啲養同唔好被醫生氹到亂做檢查嘅話都唔算洗費大嘅。但如果你自己都養唔起就算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6574c6ae3f5ec5646a5c1155280f904ece9237e1","tid":50704,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>稍為嚴重少少都破萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 係呀 想做貓奴都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚到時有咩事冇能力醫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n領養成貓囉，慳返筆絕育費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有揀隻又肥又乖嘅唐貓，無咁多病痛，同埋可以自己沖涼剪甲慳錢。<br />\n<br />\n買隻好少少嘅糧，同溝水入啲濕糧到，飲多啲水同夠營養就無咩病痛㗎啦。<br />\n<br />\n每個月儲500，夠睇醫生㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識養記得問人，小心啲養同唔好被醫生氹到亂做檢查嘅話都唔算洗費大嘅。但如果你自己都養唔起就算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果每月500我ok 最驚係佢多病痛我到時真係唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 近日睇到有隻成貓 佢一隻眼盲左好耐都冇人領養 考慮緊過埋今個月好唔好帶佢返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eca70ee385d0f1cac23dd1e3ab052849dd70308","tid":50704,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T00:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 係呀 想做貓奴都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚到時有咩事冇能力醫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n領養成貓囉，慳返筆絕育費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有揀隻又肥又乖嘅唐貓，無咁多病痛，同埋可以自己沖涼剪甲慳錢。<br />\n<br />\n買隻好少少嘅糧，同溝水入啲濕糧到，飲多啲水同夠營養就無咩病痛㗎啦。<br />\n<br />\n每個月儲500，夠睇醫生㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識養記得問人，小心啲養同唔好被醫生氹到亂做檢查嘅話都唔算洗費大嘅。但如果你自己都養唔起就算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果每月500我ok 最驚係佢多病痛我到時真係唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 近日睇到有隻成貓 佢一隻眼盲左好耐都冇人領養 考慮緊過埋今個月好唔好帶佢返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇中就去馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唐貓真係健康啲<br />\n貓最主要健康問題係腎病<br />\n要飲多啲水就無咩大問題"},{"pid":"ab63d110e44d3ca2cb2226d2bd22a1d6a10f1dfa","tid":50704,"uid":18446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:26:32.000Z","msg":"主人食咗膠落肚<br />\n做手術 $5000"},{"pid":"874ef1d8eda13f05191db190cc2754ca55b420a0","tid":50704,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockq